      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not just being tired though. it's the fact that even when i rest, the loop starts again. i do the work, i make the changes, and then 6 months later i'm right back here. it's like a glitch in the system. there's no \"step back\" that fixes a broken pattern. it feels like the only way to actually stop the cycle is to break the machine entirely.",
