      "content": "i dont think its a \"thought process\" thing. i've tried therapy, i've tried changing how i think, i've tried everything. it's just a cycle of existence. it's like being stuck in a room where the walls keep closing in no matter how much you move. everything i do just leads back to this same emptiness. the loop only ends one way, you know?",
